metadata.description:
It's a Soul Tribe Christmas <3 

Wishing everyone peace, love, and presence this holiday season.

xoxo

Lyrics:

This time of year I feel grateful
For all of the people I know
Like a kid longing for snow
I've been wishing to fill up my soul
This year I learned about patience 
It takes some water to grow
When everything's frozen
Live in the moment
It's time to let it flow

I don't need no presents under the tree
Cause I feel the presence between you and me
Doesn't it feel warm?
Opening your heart 

Open up your heart to 
Golden lights  
We’re fire side 
Its cold outside 
But its just right 
I found a new perspective 
Looking at my reflection
In the shadows 
Where the light glows 

I don't need no presents under the tree
Cause I feel the presence between you and me
Doesn't it feel warm?
Opening your heart 

Opening your heart 
Opening your heart
It doesn't have to be so hard
Opening your heart 

Vocal Arrangement by TAROT
Written by TAROT
Produced by Phinestro (pianos & guitar) & Andre Hairston (synths, bass, percussion)
Instrumental Arrangement & Percussion elements by Pete Rango 
Mixed & Mastered by Pete Rango
